    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Level 2</strong> Transmutation</p>\n<p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 1 bonus</p>\n<p><strong>Range:</strong> undefined touch</p>\n<p><strong>Components:</strong> V, S</p>\n<p><strong>Duration:</strong> 1 hour</p>\n\nYou touch a nonmagical weapon. Until the spell ends, that weapon becomes a magic weapon with a +1 bonus to attack rolls and damage rolls. The spell ends early if you cast it again.\n\n<p><strong>At Higher Levels:</strong> The bonus increases to +2 with a level 3-5 spell slot. The bonus increases to +3 with a level 6+ spell slot.</p>",
